'''''Apache 3''''' is a [[3D computer graphics|3D]] scrolling [[shoot 'em up]] [[arcade video game]] released by Tatsumi (and [[Data East]] in North America) in 1988. Players control a yellow [[AH-64 Apache]] [[helicopter]] with weapons and shoot everything in the air and on the ground.

